<item>
            <title>[HBASE-10869] Add FS_TYPE in HBaseTestingUtility configuration</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-10869</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Motivation of doing this is two-folded:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;1. local file system is more stable than `MiniDFSCluster`, so for cases only testing on HBase logic, using this may avoid unstable problems caused by DFS unstable problem.&lt;br/&gt;
1. Starting of local file systme is much faster.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Currently only a few of the testcases is switch to LFS mode for testing. Some other diff may switch more.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Implementaiton&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For `FS_TYPE_DFS`, same as before.&lt;br/&gt;
For `FS_TYPE_LFS`, use `LocalFileSystem`&lt;/p&gt;</description>
